markets.title: Will the **USD/Mexican peso exchange rate** be above 21 on February 4?
markets.rules_primary: If the Federal Reserve's H.10 report reports that the conversion between the U.S. dollar and Mexican peso on February 04, 2022 is above 21, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary:
Please note that the data is from the Federal Reserve and represents the noon buying rate on the date in question.

Data is expected to be released at 4:15 PM on February 7, 2022. The market will close at 4:10 that day. The market will expire at the sooner of the first 10:00 AM ET following the release of the data or February 18, 2022.
